Metadata: Effects of somatostatin-25 and urotensin II on lipid and carbohydrate metabolism of coho salmon, "Oncorhynchus kisutch"

Described in this report are the effects of "in vivo" administration of salmon somatostatin and synthetic urotensin II on plasma free fatty acids, plasma glucose, and plasma insulin, and on the activities of certain key metabolic enzymes in coho salmon, "Oncorhynchus kisutch."
